java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
public class AnalyzeStepPanel
extends StepPanel

This panel represents a single step in a multi-step process, both graphically and logically. It encapsulates all the necessary graphical elements and program logic needed for this step, and provides access methods for necessary data to be passed along to the next step. Specifically, it handles Analysis Method processing for the JGAAP program.
